1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 10=

4
00:00:25,239 --> 00:00:26,039
Father!

5
00:00:26,879 --> 00:00:27,679
Father!

6
00:00:29,399 --> 00:00:30,199
Father!

7
00:00:30,839 --> 00:00:31,800
You little brat.

8
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:34,000
Save your strength.

9
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,759
Your meridians are severed.

10
00:00:35,759 --> 00:00:36,880
Your cultivation is gone.

11
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:38,679
You're completely powerless now.

12
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:43,119
Father! Father!

13
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,560
I'll kill him!

14
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:47,039
I'll kill him!

15
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:48,560
I'll kill him!

16
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,240
Masters of the Thirty-Six Caves
of Miaojiang, answer me!

17
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:55,679
- At your command!
- From this day forward,

18
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:58,200
Peng Dasheng is
the Holy Envoy of the Wudu Sect.

19
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:01,000
All three thousand disciples
of the Thirty-Six Caves

20
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,000
will answer to Peng Dasheng alone.

21
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:05,480
Anyone who stands against him

22
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:08,159
stands against all of Miaojiang.

23
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,359
Yes!

24
00:01:17,159 --> 00:01:18,040
Duan Qingyao,

25
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,959
this is Gusu,

26
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,280
not Miaojiang.

27
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:24,920
Even if it means taking on
the entire Wudu Sect,

28
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:28,079
that guy dies today.

29
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:31,280
What if Nongxiao Pavilion
stands with him?

30
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,799
The Shuzhong Tang Clan is in too.

31
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:34,799
Count Cangshan Sect in.

32
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:36,719
- And Kongtong Sect.
- And Xiaoyao Sect.

33
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,719
Quanzhen Sect too.

34
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:45,359
And me! And me!

35
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:45,840
You...

36
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,079
And me! And me!

37
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:54,120
And me! And me! Me!

38
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,959
The Kunlun Sect stands with him too.

39
00:01:55,959 --> 00:02:00,400
And me! And me!

40
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:03,519
Kun Zhongyu... You...

41
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,799
What are you waiting for?

42
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:08,680
What are you waiting for? Get them!

43
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,560
Sir,

44
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,319
Mr. Lin is in critical condition.

45
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,879
We need to get him home for treatment.

46
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:22,560
You dare disobey me?

47
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,560
I wouldn't dare.

48
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,039
Lin Dun,

49
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,879
do you really want
the entire martial world against you?

50
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:28,800
I...

51
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:36,639
Mr. Lin!

52
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,960
Son, let's go home.

53
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,120
Father!

54
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,319
Father!

55
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,199
Wait.

56
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,039
Mr. Lin,

57
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,280
I expect you to keep your word.

58
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:04,919
From today on, Huxiao Manor will leave
the martial world for good.

59
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,199
If I ever catch

60
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,319
you or your son

61
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,599
causing trouble again,

62
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,840
I promise

63
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:14,680
the Lin family will meet
the same fate as the Sihai Gang.

64
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,560
Peng Dasheng, you've gone too far!

65
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:22,360
Lin Dun, Peng Dasheng has shown you
more mercy than you deserve.

66
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,919
If it were up to me,

67
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,639
you wouldn't be leaving here alive.

68
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:32,240
Lin Dun,

69
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,319
get out of here.

70
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,360
If my young master changes his mind,

71
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,000
you're as good as dead.

72
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:43,719
(Peng Dasheng, one day,)

73
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:46,680
(I'll tear you limb from limb.)

74
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:47,719
Let's go.

75
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:01,280
That nuisance is finally gone.

76
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:02,759
Dasheng.

77
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:03,479
Guys.

78
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,120
You hid it well.

79
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,080
All right, let's continue.

80
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,840
You just reached
the fourth rank, didn't you?

81
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,599
I've never heard of anything like it.

82
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,240
My master said

83
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,520
advancing your cultivation
is like scaling a sheer cliff.

84
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:16,079
Without the right opportunity,
it can't be rushed.

85
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:18,439
Today proves he was right.

86
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:22,920
It took me five full years

87
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:25,000
to rise from
the sixth rank to the fifth.

88
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,160
I was, well...

89
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,279
One of the fastest

90
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:31,160
martial artists my age.

91
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:33,439
Yet you did it in less than two hours.

92
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,360
You're blessed with an opportunity

93
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,480
the rest of us can only envy.

94
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,879
Then stop envying me.

95
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,040
Everyone,

96
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,240
we had a little incident

97
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,439
just now.

98
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,279
But perhaps

99
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:47,279
it was a blessing

100
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,480
in disguise.

101
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,639
It proves

102
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:53,519
just how fierce the competition is
at this martial tournament.

103
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,079
Mr. Peng,

104
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,160
as the undisputed champion

105
00:04:58,160 --> 00:05:00,000
of this martial tournament,

106
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,959
do you have anything to say?

107
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,800
I have a question for Miss Murong.

108
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:12,000
Mr. Peng,

109
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,519
aren't you a little impatient?

110
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:18,279
Once you're alone with Miss Murong

111
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:20,399
on your wedding night,

112
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:22,839
you can ask her anything.

113
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,160
Why ask now?

114
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,680
This question matters.

115
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:28,560
I need to ask it in front of everyone.

116
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:31,759
Mr. Peng, we don't mind hearing

117
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:34,639
a little sweet talk from you,

118
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:37,639
but Miss Murong
comes from a distinguished family.

119
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:39,959
She may be too embarrassed.

120
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:42,879
Take my advice, young man.

121
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,680
Young women can be shy.

122
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,240
Some things

123
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,959
are far better said

124
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:50,639
in private

125
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:53,079
than in front of a crowd.

126
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:54,279
Exactly.

127
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,759
Mr. Bai is famous

128
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:58,600
for understanding women.

129
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,959
You've both misunderstood.

130
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:05,000
This isn't sweet talk.

131
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,120
Miss Murong said I had ties
to Murong Manor.

132
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:10,120
I'd like to know what she meant.

133
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:11,240
Please explain.

134
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,319
My father already told me.

135
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,800
That marriage agreement was
only my grandfather's passing joke.

136
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:22,920
With no clan or status to speak of,

137
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,519
you expect to be
part of the Murong family?

138
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,720
Murong Bingqing,

139
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:29,439
I was planning
to leave Gusu today anyway.

140
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:32,839
But now, I've changed my mind.

141
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:36,480
I'll definitely attend

142
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,680
your martial arts marriage contest
tomorrow.

143
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:40,319
And I'll defeat everyone there.

144
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,360
Then, I'll make you say

145
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,720
in front of everyone,

146
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,959
"Dear,

147
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,600
I was wrong."

148
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,800
Peng Dasheng,

149
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,879
I know exactly what you're after.

150
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,399
You just want me to admit

151
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,879
that we were once engaged

152
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:04,240
so you can humiliate me, don't you?

153
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,759
You're the one
who kept refusing to admit it.

154
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:09,000
My young master

155
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,839
only wants justice.

156
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:11,879
Fine.

157
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,199
Then I'll set the record straight.

158
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:15,959
Yes.

159
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,360
I did publicly

160
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,040
break off our engagement

161
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,959
and threaten to drive you out of Gusu.

162
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:23,600
Now everyone knows.

163
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,720
Are you satisfied?

164
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,959
You broke your word first.

165
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,839
Don't act like the victim.

166
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,000
I was born
into a prominent martial family.

167
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,800
An arranged marriage was inevitable.

168
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,639
Back then,

169
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,959
you were just a nobody
from the countryside,

170
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,079
with no power or status.

171
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,439
What would you have done

172
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,199
in my place?

173
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,879
What I would've done doesn't matter.

174
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:53,800
What matters

175
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,279
is that I would never become

176
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:57,959
vain and heartless.

177
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,040
And I would never use
my own circumstances

178
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,600
as an excuse to trample
on someone else's dignity.

179
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,519
Murong Bingqing,

180
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,399
we actually came to Gusu

181
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,600
to break off the engagement.

182
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,319
I only changed my mind

183
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:09,680
after you tried

184
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,879
to drive us out of the city.

185
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:12,879
The martial tournament was my idea.

186
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,639
That's right.

187
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:20,279
When my father was struggling
in the martial world,

188
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,759
he did agree
to an engagement for Bingqing.

189
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,800
Mr. Murong,

190
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,800
since you admit

191
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,720
your daughter and I were once engaged,

192
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,920
and I won today's martial tournament,

193
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,080
asking her

194
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,440
to call me her dear

195
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,679
in front of everyone

196
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,759
isn't too much, is it?

197
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,720
I told you.

198
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,000
If I won,

199
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,799
you're gonna say,

200
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,960
"Dear, I was wrong."

201
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,360
Mr. Peng,

202
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:55,399
if Bingqing apologizes,

203
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:58,159
will you promise
never to bring this up again?

204
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,120
You have my word.

205
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,159
Fine.

206
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,519
Bingqing, apologize to him.

207
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,120
Father...

208
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,360
Do as I say.

209
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,000
Dear,

210
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,720
I was wrong.

211
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,960
Mr. Peng,

212
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:26,200
when do you plan to marry
into the Murong family?

213
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,519
Mr. Murong, you've misunderstood.

214
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,360
I never intended to marry her.

215
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:36,799
Peng Dasheng.

216
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,919
You only wanted
to humiliate me in public, didn't you?

217
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,120
Murong Bingqing,

218
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:44,879
I'm not the man you truly want to marry.

219
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,720
Besides,
my heart belongs to someone else.

220
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,200
Xiaojiu.

221
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:20,600
- I'm done here. Let's go.
- Okay.

222
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:22,799
Wait!

223
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,600
Peng Dasheng,

224
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:29,480
take back what you just said,

225
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,559
and I'll pretend none of this happened.

226
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:34,759
Your engagement to Bingqing
can still go ahead.

227
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:41,240
And if I refuse?

228
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:44,440
You humiliated my daughter in public.

229
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:45,240
Do you really think

230
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,480
I'll let you walk away that easily?

231
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:53,000
Disciples of Miaojiang, heed my command!

232
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,039
At your command!

233
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,720
Miss Duan, thank you.

234
00:10:59,279 --> 00:11:01,480
But this is between
the Murong family and me.

235
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:02,720
I'll handle it myself.

236
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,200
Boy,

237
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:16,960
I admit I underestimated you
until today.

238
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,320
You've barely entered the martial world,

239
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,960
yet you killed
the Northern Evil Duo of the Demon Sect.

240
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:25,120
I see great promise in you now.

241
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,440
Bingqing is my only daughter.

242
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,200
If you marry her,

243
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:35,840
this vast estate will be yours someday.

244
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,960
Countless young martial artists

245
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:40,799
would do anything for this chance.

246
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:43,600
Are you really giving it up so easily?

247
00:11:46,159 --> 00:11:47,200
Mr. Murong,

248
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:49,200
I grew up deep in the mountains.

249
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,399
I've always lived freely

250
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:52,320
and hate being bound by rules.

251
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,799
Everything you just offered me

252
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,879
would only tie me down.

253
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,360
As for this engagement,

254
00:11:58,919 --> 00:11:59,840
I must refuse.

255
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,200
If you never intended to marry Bingqing,

256
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:06,799
you shouldn't have entered
the martial tournament.

257
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,919
Since you won't accept my offer,

258
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:12,240
don't blame me for what happens next.

259
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:27,039
Where did you get that soul jade?

260
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:31,120
My father left it to me.

261
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:36,399
(I can't believe he's that man's son.)

262
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,639
Go.

263
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,279
Mr. Murong, please reconsider!

264
00:12:48,279 --> 00:12:48,840
This...

265
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,720
Go, Peng Dasheng.

266
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:56,360
From now on,

267
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,639
the Murong family and you are even.

268
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,519
Thank you, Mr. Murong.

269
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:03,000
I'll take my leave.

270
00:13:03,919 --> 00:13:04,720
Let's go.

271
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:20,080
Miss, don't go outside!

272
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,240
It's dangerous out there.

273
00:13:23,279 --> 00:13:24,000
What's going on?

274
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:24,799
What happened?

275
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:25,840
(Martial Tournament)
It went dark.

276
00:13:27,559 --> 00:13:28,639
It went dark all of a sudden.

277
00:13:39,039 --> 00:13:40,279
Nether Marionette.

278
00:13:45,879 --> 00:13:49,320
Such a soft, delicate young man.

279
00:13:49,879 --> 00:13:51,200
How tempting.

280
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:57,559
How about letting me have a taste?

281
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:01,039
Get out of my way, old woman.

282
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:03,120
He's mine.

283
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:13,860
♪Come on♪

284
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:19,060
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

285
00:14:21,020 --> 00:14:23,980
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

286
00:14:24,260 --> 00:14:27,180
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

287
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:30,260
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

288
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:33,260
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

289
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:36,740
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

290
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

291
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:43,060
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

292
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:45,980
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

293
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:49,860
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

294
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:52,900
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

295
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:58,580
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

296
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,020
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

297
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:04,100
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

298
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:07,220
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

299
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:11,020
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

300
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:13,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

301
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:16,780
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

302
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:20,220
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

303
00:15:20,260 --> 00:15:24,540
♪I am my own king♪

304
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:39,180
♪I emerge into the world♪

305
00:15:39,180 --> 00:15:40,940
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

306
00:15:40,940 --> 00:15:42,300
♪My pride is my trump card♪

307
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:44,100
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

308
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,500
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

309
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:47,260
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

310
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:48,780
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

311
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,500
♪I dare to break every rule♪

312
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:51,820
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

313
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:53,660
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

314
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:54,900
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

315
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:57,140
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

316
00:15:57,140 --> 00:15:58,660
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

317
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,260
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

318
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:01,860
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

319
00:16:01,860 --> 00:16:03,580
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

320
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:05,300
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

321
00:16:05,300 --> 00:16:06,660
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

322
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:08,300
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

323
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:09,780
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

324
00:16:09,780 --> 00:16:11,500
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

325
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:13,100
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

326
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,660
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

327
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:18,980
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

328
00:16:18,980 --> 00:16:21,140
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

329
00:16:21,140 --> 00:16:23,740
♪Let me write the legend♪

330
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:31,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

331
00:16:31,180 --> 00:16:34,500
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

332
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:36,980
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

333
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:41,060
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

334
00:16:41,420 --> 00:16:44,020
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

335
00:16:44,140 --> 00:16:46,500
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

336
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:49,540
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

337
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:54,580
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
